{"id":"963f94e06be6912a185bb16c7bdc84971433124f","url":"https://fellowgeek.github.io/mcp-speak","title":"Speak MCP | Voice Interface for Agents","site_name":"Buzzing","source":"fellowgeek.github.io","byline":null,"excerpt":"Config copied to clipboard","content_html":"<DIV class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"toast\">\n        \n        <p><span id=\"toast-message\">Config copied to clipboard</span>\n    </p></div><div id=\"main-nav\">\n                \n                <p><span><span>MCP</span> Speak</span>\n            </p></div><DIV>\n        <p><span>\n                <span></span>\n                <span></span>\n            </span>\n            MacOS Native\n        </p>\n        \n        <p>\n            A specialized Model Context Protocol server for MacOS. Give your agents direct access to the system voice engine for real-time interaction.\n        </p>\n        \n    </DIV><DIV>\n\n        <!-- Installation -->\n        <section id=\"install\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>Setup Guide</h2>\n                <p>Follow these steps to initialize your voice server.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n                <!-- Step 1 -->\n                <div>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>1</p>\n                        </div>\n                    <h3>Clone Repository</h3>\n                    <p>Fetch the code and navigate into the project directory.</p>\n                    <p><code>git clone https://github.com/fellowgeek/mcp-speak.git &amp;&amp; cd mcp-speak</code>\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Step 2 -->\n                <div>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>2</p>\n                        </div>\n                    <h3>Run Setup Wizard</h3>\n                    <p>Configures your persona, permissions, and virtual environment automatically.</p>\n                    <p><code>python3 setup.py</code>\n                    </p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Configuration -->\n        <div id=\"config\">\n                <h2>Manual Integration (Optional)</h2>\n                <p>Running <code>python3 setup.py</code> configures your client automatically. Below are manual JSON reference snippets.</p>\n            </div>\n\n        <!-- Personas -->\n        <section id=\"personas\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>Personality Profiles</h2>\n                <p>Standard agents are boring. Select a persona to see how it modifies your agent's spoken behavior.</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n                <!-- Sarcastic Senior -->\n                <div id=\"p-senior\" onclick=\"selectPersona('senior', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/sarcastic_senior.webp\" alt=\"Sarcastic Senior\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Sarcastic Senior</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Eager Intern -->\n                <div id=\"p-intern\" onclick=\"selectPersona('intern', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/over_eager_intern.webp\" alt=\"Eager Intern\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Eager Intern</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Existential Emo -->\n                <div id=\"p-emo\" onclick=\"selectPersona('emo', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/existential_emo.webp\" alt=\"Existential Emo\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Existential Emo</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Pun Master -->\n                <div id=\"p-pun\" onclick=\"selectPersona('pun', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/pun_master.webp\" alt=\"Pun Master\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Pun Master</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Tech Priest -->\n                <div id=\"p-priest\" onclick=\"selectPersona('priest', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/tech_priest.webp\" alt=\"Tech Priest\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Tech Priest</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Agent Smith -->\n                <div id=\"p-smith\" onclick=\"selectPersona('smith', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/agent_smith.webp\" alt=\"Agent Smith\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Agent Smith</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Gothic Poet -->\n                <div id=\"p-poet\" onclick=\"selectPersona('poet', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/poet.webp\" alt=\"Gothic Poet\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>Gothic Poet</h3>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n                    <div>\n                        <h3 id=\"persona-title\">Initialize Persona</h3>\n                        <p id=\"persona-desc\">Select a character above to view its communication protocol.</p>\n\n                        <div>\n                            <p><label>User Preference</label>\n                                \n                            </p>\n                            <p>\n                                <label for=\"include-base\">Include Base Guidelines</label>\n                            </p>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div>\n                            <p>Updates dynamically based on selection</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <p><label>Generated AGENTS.md</label>\n                        \n                    </p>\n                </div>\n        </section>\n\n    </DIV><div>\n            <div>\n                \n                <p><span>MCP Speak</span>\n            </p></div>\n            <p>\n                Designed for MacOS systems. This project provides a bridge between Model Context Protocol clients and local speech synthesis engines.\n            </p>\n            \n        </div></DIV>","content_text":"Config copied to clipboard MCP Speak MacOS Native A specialized Model Context Protocol server for MacOS. Give your agents direct access to the system voice engine for real-time interaction. Setup Guide Follow these steps to initialize your voice server. 1 Clone Repository Fetch the code and navigate into the project directory. git clone https://github.com/fellowgeek/mcp-speak.git && cd mcp-speak 2 Run Setup Wizard Configures your persona, permissions, and virtual environment automatically. python3 setup.py Manual Integration (Optional) Running python3 setup.py configures your client automatically. Below are manual JSON reference snippets. Personality Profiles Standard agents are boring. Select a persona to see how it modifies your agent's spoken behavior. Sarcastic Senior Eager Intern Existential Emo Pun Master Tech Priest Agent Smith Gothic Poet Initialize Persona Select a character above to view its communication protocol. User Preference Include Base Guidelines Updates dynamically based on selection Generated AGENTS.md MCP Speak Designed for MacOS systems. This project provides a bridge between Model Context Protocol clients and local speech synthesis engines.","fetched_at":"2026-07-21T12:37:37.220Z","ok":true,"blocks":[{"html_en":"<p><span id=\"toast-message\">Config copied to clipboard</span>\n    </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Config copied to clipboard","zh":"配置已复制到剪贴板"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span><span>MCP</span> Speak</span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"MCP Speak","zh":"MCP 发言"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>\n                <span></span>\n                <span></span>\n            </span>\n            MacOS Native\n        </p>","sentences":[{"en":"MacOS Native","zh":"MacOS 原生"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n            A specialized Model Context Protocol server for MacOS. Give your agents direct access to the system voice engine for real-time interaction.\n        </p>","sentences":[{"en":"A specialized Model Context Protocol server for MacOS.","zh":"适用于 MacOS 的专用模型上下文协议服务器。"},{"en":"Give your agents direct access to the system voice engine for real-time interaction.","zh":"让您的座席直接访问系统语音引擎以进行实时交互。"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>Setup Guide</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Setup Guide","zh":"设置指南"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Follow these steps to initialize your voice server.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Follow these steps to initialize your voice server.","zh":"请按照以下步骤初始化您的语音服务器。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Clone Repository</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Clone Repository","zh":"克隆存储库"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Fetch the code and navigate into the project directory.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Fetch the code and navigate into the project directory.","zh":"获取代码并导航到项目目录。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><code>git clone https://github.com/fellowgeek/mcp-speak.git &amp;&amp; cd mcp-speak</code>\n                    </p>","sentences":[{"en":"git clone https://github.com/fellowgeek/mcp-speak.git && cd mcp-speak","zh":"git 克隆 https://github.com/fellowgeek/mcp-speak.git && cd mcp-speak"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Run Setup Wizard</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Run Setup Wizard","zh":"运行安装向导"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Configures your persona, permissions, and virtual environment automatically.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Configures your persona, permissions, and virtual environment automatically.","zh":"自动配置您的角色、权限和虚拟环境。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><code>python3 setup.py</code>\n                    </p>","sentences":[{"en":"python3 setup.py","zh":"python3安装程序.py"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>Manual Integration (Optional)</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Manual Integration (Optional)","zh":"手动集成（可选）"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Running <code>python3 setup.py</code> configures your client automatically. Below are manual JSON reference snippets.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Running python3 setup.py configures your client automatically.","zh":"运行 python3 setup.py 会自动配置您的客户端。"},{"en":"Below are manual JSON reference snippets.","zh":"以下是手动 JSON 参考片段。"}]},{"html_en":"<h2>Personality Profiles</h2>","sentences":[{"en":"Personality Profiles","zh":"性格简介"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Standard agents are boring. Select a persona to see how it modifies your agent's spoken behavior.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Standard agents are boring.","zh":"标准特工很无聊。"},{"en":"Select a persona to see how it modifies your agent's spoken behavior.","zh":"选择一个角色以查看它如何修改座席的言语行为。"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Sarcastic Senior</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Sarcastic Senior","zh":"讽刺前辈"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Eager Intern</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Eager Intern","zh":"热心实习生"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Existential Emo</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Existential Emo","zh":"存在主义情绪"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Pun Master</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Pun Master","zh":"连大师"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Tech Priest</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Tech Priest","zh":"科技牧师"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Agent Smith</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Agent Smith","zh":"史密斯特工"}]},{"html_en":"<h3>Gothic Poet</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Gothic Poet","zh":"哥特诗人"}]},{"html_en":"<h3 id=\"persona-title\">Initialize Persona</h3>","sentences":[{"en":"Initialize Persona","zh":"初始化角色"}]},{"html_en":"<p id=\"persona-desc\">Select a character above to view its communication protocol.</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Select a character above to view its communication protocol.","zh":"选择上面的字符可查看其通信协议。"}]},{"html_en":"<p><label>User Preference</label>\n                                \n                            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"User Preference","zh":"用户偏好"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n                                <label for=\"include-base\">Include Base Guidelines</label>\n                            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Include Base Guidelines","zh":"包括基本指南"}]},{"html_en":"<p>Updates dynamically based on selection</p>","sentences":[{"en":"Updates dynamically based on selection","zh":"根据选择动态更新"}]},{"html_en":"<p><label>Generated AGENTS.md</label>\n                        \n                    </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Generated AGENTS.md","zh":"生成的 AGENTS.md"}]},{"html_en":"<p><span>MCP Speak</span>\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"MCP Speak","zh":"MCP 发言"}]},{"html_en":"<p>\n                Designed for MacOS systems. This project provides a bridge between Model Context Protocol clients and local speech synthesis engines.\n            </p>","sentences":[{"en":"Designed for MacOS systems.","zh":"专为 MacOS 系统设计。"},{"en":"This project provides a bridge between Model Context Protocol clients and local speech synthesis engines.","zh":"该项目提供了模型上下文协议客户端和本地语音合成引擎之间的桥梁。"}]}],"translated":true,"content_html_zh":"<div class=\"page\" id=\"readability-page-1\"><div id=\"toast\">\n        \n        <p>配置已复制到剪贴板</p></div><div id=\"main-nav\">\n                \n                <p>MCP 发言</p></div><div>\n        <p>MacOS 原生</p>\n        \n        <p>适用于 MacOS 的专用模型上下文协议服务器。 让您的座席直接访问系统语音引擎以进行实时交互。</p>\n        \n    </div><div>\n\n        <!-- Installation -->\n        <section id=\"install\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>设置指南</h2>\n                <p>请按照以下步骤初始化您的语音服务器。</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n                <!-- Step 1 -->\n                <div>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>1</p>\n                        </div>\n                    <h3>克隆存储库</h3>\n                    <p>获取代码并导航到项目目录。</p>\n                    <p>git 克隆 https://github.com/fellowgeek/mcp-speak.git &amp;&amp; cd mcp-speak</p>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Step 2 -->\n                <div>\n                    <div>\n                        <p>2</p>\n                        </div>\n                    <h3>运行安装向导</h3>\n                    <p>自动配置您的角色、权限和虚拟环境。</p>\n                    <p>python3安装程序.py</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- Configuration -->\n        <div id=\"config\">\n                <h2>手动集成（可选）</h2>\n                <p>运行 python3 setup.py 会自动配置您的客户端。 以下是手动 JSON 参考片段。</p>\n            </div>\n\n        <!-- Personas -->\n        <section id=\"personas\">\n            <div>\n                <h2>性格简介</h2>\n                <p>标准特工很无聊。 选择一个角色以查看它如何修改座席的言语行为。</p>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n                <!-- Sarcastic Senior -->\n                <div id=\"p-senior\" onclick=\"selectPersona('senior', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/sarcastic_senior.webp\" alt=\"Sarcastic Senior\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>讽刺前辈</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Eager Intern -->\n                <div id=\"p-intern\" onclick=\"selectPersona('intern', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/over_eager_intern.webp\" alt=\"Eager Intern\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>热心实习生</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Existential Emo -->\n                <div id=\"p-emo\" onclick=\"selectPersona('emo', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/existential_emo.webp\" alt=\"Existential Emo\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>存在主义情绪</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Pun Master -->\n                <div id=\"p-pun\" onclick=\"selectPersona('pun', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/pun_master.webp\" alt=\"Pun Master\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>连大师</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Tech Priest -->\n                <div id=\"p-priest\" onclick=\"selectPersona('priest', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/tech_priest.webp\" alt=\"Tech Priest\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>科技牧师</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Agent Smith -->\n                <div id=\"p-smith\" onclick=\"selectPersona('smith', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/agent_smith.webp\" alt=\"Agent Smith\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>史密斯特工</h3>\n                </div>\n\n                <!-- Gothic Poet -->\n                <div id=\"p-poet\" onclick=\"selectPersona('poet', this)\">\n                    <p><img src=\"images/poet.webp\" alt=\"Gothic Poet\">\n                    </p>\n                    <h3>哥特诗人</h3>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div>\n                    <div>\n                        <h3 id=\"persona-title\">初始化角色</h3>\n                        <p id=\"persona-desc\">选择上面的字符可查看其通信协议。</p>\n\n                        <div>\n                            <p>用户偏好</p>\n                            <p>包括基本指南</p>\n                        </div>\n\n                        <div>\n                            <p>根据选择动态更新</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <p>生成的 AGENTS.md</p>\n                </div>\n        </section>\n\n    </div><div>\n            <div>\n                \n                <p>MCP 发言</p></div>\n            <p>专为 MacOS 系统设计。 该项目提供了模型上下文协议客户端和本地语音合成引擎之间的桥梁。</p>\n            \n        </div></div>"}